                <h2 class="mb-3">What is Panchakarma?</h2>
                <p class="lead">Panchakarma is the cornerstone of Ayurvedic healing - a comprehensive detoxification and rejuvenation program that cleanses the body at the cellular level.</p>
                <p>This ancient therapeutic system consists of five main procedures designed to eliminate toxins (ama) and restore balance to the doshas (Vata, Pitta, Kapha).</p>
