                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">1. Vamana (Emesis Therapy)</h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Controlled vomiting therapy to eliminate excess Kapha dosha and toxins from the upper respiratory and gastrointestinal tract.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <div class="card h-100">
